## Future Feature: Chapter-Based CSV Export for Vocab List

Later, add CSV export to the book-specific Vocab List page.

The first version should be CSV only, not PDF. Students should be able to choose a chapter from the current book’s saved vocabulary, then download a CSV for that chapter.

Suggested export options:

* All chapters
* Each chapter found in the saved vocab rows
* No chapter, if any words do not have chapter data

The export should use vocab rows already loaded on the page and should not add a new API route for the first pass. It should not change Supabase queries, ownership checks, RLS assumptions, save/delete behavior, or vocab loading behavior.

Suggested CSV columns:

* Book Title
* Chapter
* Page
* Surface
* Reading
* Meaning
* JLPT
* Common
* Hidden in Reading Support
* Created At

PDF export can stay deferred as a future polish feature.
